{"id": "a33830cef2272aa3d774d44a2d3e77fc762130c28d60379c3de1ca9b445f5b0f", "item_id": "3ac31554be:0", "text": "Here is an example of exporting Ri Attributes (e.g. Ri Round Curve) to an Alembic File for reading into RenderMan for Maya (RfM), which expects rman__ and not ri_ as Houdini has historically used."}
{"id": "0452bee237331c0d2cdbea180556a9b3f05bd2aee3848a7357ed52cc9ad62018", "item_id": "3ac31554be:1", "text": "Add an"}
{"id": "b533cc6390af961f150aa3f1dbaa11fe3c78da924369167cc83e83d3dc42b1d3", "item_id": "3ac31554be:2", "text": "AttributeCreate"}
{"id": "4a2db0d103b052cec13b0bc470fabd2b922f4dee2e6778dfc1f2649d3d33e330", "item_id": "3ac31554be:4", "text": "Name it as how it is named in RenderMan for Maya, e.g. rman__riattr__dice_roundcurve"}
{"id": "46d83ae08c25b597db96d5b6b7426ad6364ec2935a70d6cb836950a3fed98b03", "item_id": "3ac31554be:5", "text": "Set the Class to"}
{"id": "fb5f27d5457c464102286366ef3827b11923e7f3aa1faa7eea95249e36a39abf", "item_id": "3ac31554be:6", "text": "Detail"}
{"id": "8b77caf9bbdfb61b61766e2ed288d6885c2fae4762709c0aa025a8ec16f0421b", "item_id": "3ac31554be:7", "text": "Set the Value expression to the Ri Attribute (e.g. ri_roundcurve)"}
{"id": "e99b9a151b2beb001b7bcad41cfe63053af19df0e429a8aef631d49e41ee8dce", "item_id": "3ac31554be:8", "text": "You can download this example here:"}
{"id": "6df9180ca15414deb6b7dcd31e3aa955122d3d1efff5c19ec6ba15de12df2f04", "item_id": "3ac31554be:9", "text": "curves_alembicattr.hip"}
{"id": "00835f493c74d06357eab8f7b67683780b6cc26ebfe46761680e2172766b5ea9", "item_id": "3ac31554be:10", "text": "When you read the alembic file into RfM, you will see the Round Curve attribute with the setting from Houdini."}
